\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Sudoku Generator and Visualizer\
\
This project generates Sudoku puzzles of varying difficulty levels and visualizes them as colorful grids. It uses Python's `PIL` library to create an image representation of the puzzle, with each number mapped to a specific color.\
\
## Features\
- Generate a fully solved Sudoku board.\
- Create puzzles with customizable difficulty (based on the number of clues).\
- Visualize Sudoku puzzles as images with distinct colors for each number.\
- Print the board in a human-readable format in the console.\
\
